        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer611815235" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4181230371571271214">&quot;The Mouse and the Motorcycle&quot; is a book about a mouse named Ralph who lives in a hotel. One day a family come into the apartment where Ralph lives. One boy has some toy cars and one is a motorcycle. When the family is gone Ralph decides to take the motorcycle for a ride. Ralph ends up falling into a wastebasket. When the family comes back the child finds Ralph. The two are able to talk to each other, and they become friends. Later in the book Ralph loses the motorcylce and the child becomes ill</span>
  <span id="freeText4181230371571271214" style="display:none">"The Mouse and the Motorcycle" is a book about a mouse named Ralph who lives in a hotel. One day a family come into the apartment where Ralph lives. One boy has some toy cars and one is a motorcycle. When the family is gone Ralph decides to take the motorcycle for a ride. Ralph ends up falling into a wastebasket. When the family comes back the child finds Ralph. The two are able to talk to each other, and they become friends. Later in the book Ralph loses the motorcylce and the child becomes ill. You have to read the book to see what happens next. I recommend this book for young adults who like adventure and fiction. </span>
